  "industry_note": "PEKK (Polyetherketoneketone) — PAEK family (PEEK + PEKK). PEEK 보다 ether/ketone 비율 다름 (PEEK 60/40, PEKK 50/50) → Tg 162°C (PEEK 143°C) / Tm 305-360°C (T/I ratio 의존). max service 250-260°C continuous (PEEK 와 동등). σy 90-110 / UTS 100-115 / El 25-50% / E 3.8-4.1 GPa / ρ 1.30 g/cc. PEKK-CF (Arkema/Solvay): σy 120-150, E 12-15. **** 항공 AM SLS (3D Systems VICTREX HT, Stratasys NovaSpire), 의료 임플란트 (FDA approved Oxpekk)."
